abstract: The power company was unable to find a buyer for the Kewaunee Power Station, which was deemed economically impractical in light of falling demand and the low price of natural gas.
snippet: The power company was unable to find a buyer for the Kewaunee Power Station, which was deemed economically impractical in light of falling demand and the low price of natural gas.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The owner of a small nuclear reactor in Wisconsin said Monday that it would close the Kewaunee Power Station  early next year because it was unable to find a buyer and the plant was no longer economically viable.

headline.main: Wisconsin Nuclear Reactor to Be Closed
headline.print_headline: Wisconsin Nuclear Reactor To Be Closed
